              </article>

              <article class="cardctx__variant">
                <p class="cardctx__variant-label">B · Compact feature / media CTA</p>
                <div class="cardctx__fixed-grid cardctx__fixed-grid--feature">
                  <a href="#" class="cardctx__feature-card cardctx__feature-card--compact">
                    <div class="cardctx__feature-card-surface">
                      <div class="cardctx__feature-card-bg cardctx__feature-card-bg--tile" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                      <div class="cardctx__feature-card-scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                      <div class="cardctx__feature-card-content">
                        <p class="cardctx__eyebrow cardctx__eyebrow--on-dark">{featureCompact.eyebrow}</p>
                        <h3>{featureCompact.title}</h3>
                        <p class="cardctx__feature-card-copy">{featureCompact.copy}</p>
                        <span class="cardctx__feature-cta cardctx__feature-cta--compact">{featureCompact.cta}</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </a>
                  <a href="#" class="cardctx__feature-card cardctx__feature-card--compact">
                    <div class="cardctx__feature-card-surface">
                      <div class="cardctx__feature-card-bg cardctx__feature-card-bg--tile-alt" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                      <div class="cardctx__feature-card-scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                      <div class="cardctx__feature-card-content">
                        <p class="cardctx__eyebrow cardctx__eyebrow--on-dark">Tips</p>
                        <h3>Rengjøring uten stress</h3>
                        <p class="cardctx__feature-card-copy">En enkel rutine.</p>
                        <span class="cardctx__feature-cta cardctx__feature-cta--compact">Les tips</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cardctx__notes">
            <article>
              <h4>What to evaluate</h4>
              <p>
                Is ghost CTA affordance clear without whole-card shadow? Does this feel like feature/promo —
                not hub navigation?
              </p>
            </article>
            <article>
              <h4>Decision needed</h4>
              <p>Where does feature/media CTA belong vs standard hub/article cards?</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cardctx__panel" aria-labelledby="summary-heading">
          <p class="cardctx__kicker">Decision summary</p>
          <h2 id="summary-heading">Decision summary after QA revision</h2>
          <ul class="cardctx__list">
            {decisionSummary.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="cardctx__panel" aria-labelledby="open-heading">
          <p class="cardctx__kicker">Open decisions</p>
          <h2 id="open-heading">Still needs review</h2>
          <ul class="cardctx__list">
            {openDecisions.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="cardctx__panel" aria-labelledby="verify-heading">
          <p class="cardctx__kicker">What to verify next</p>
          <h2 id="verify-heading">Thomas QA focus</h2>
          <ul class="cardctx__list">
            {verifyNext.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="cardctx__panel" aria-labelledby="deps-heading">
          <p class="cardctx__kicker">Dependencies</p>
          <h2 id="deps-heading">Before #125</h2>
          <div class="cardctx__dependencies">
            {dependencyNotes.map((dep) => (
              <article>
                <strong>{dep.title}</strong>
                <p>{dep.note}</p>
              </article>
            ))}
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <style>
    [data-card-context-page] {
      --p-deep: #134d6a;
      --p-magenta: #ff55b0;
      --p-ink: #111827;
      --p-dark: #020617;
      --p-dark-panel: #071827;
      --p-muted: #6b7280;
      --p-light: #ffffff;
      --p-subtle: #f8fafc;
      --p-reading-paper: #ffffff;
      --p-radius: 8px;
      --p-surface-hover: 0 14px 32px rgb(15 23 42 / 0.08);
      --p-surface-lift: translateY(-2px);

      min-height: 100vh;
      max-width: 76rem;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem 3rem;
      background: var(--p-light);
